<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h1><%= @market.name %></h1>

<div class="container">
  <p>
    이미지
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>위치</strong>
    <%= @market.address %><br>

    <strong>영업시간</strong>
    <%= @market.open %><br>

    <strong>주차</strong>
    <% if @market.parking == true %>
      가능
    <% else %>
      불가
    <% end %>
    <br>

    <strong>전화번호</strong>
    <%= @market.tel %><br>

    <strong>휴일</strong>
    <%= @market.closed %><br>
  </p>
</div>

<p>
  가게 목록(사진이랑 설명, 없으면 요기요 대체 사진)
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>사진</th>
        <th>가게이름(대표메뉴)</th>
        <th>부가설명(자유)</th>
        <th>전화번호</th>
        <th colspan="3"></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>

    <tbody>
      <% @market.shops.each do |shop| %>
        <tr>
          <td>사진</td>
          <td><%= shop.name %></td>
          <td>부가설명(자유)</td>
          <td><%= shop.tel %></td>
          <td><%= link_to 'Show', shop %></td>
          <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_shop_path(shop) %></td>
          <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', shop, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</p>

<p>
  전체 후기 중 best 3개, 전체 평점
</p>

<%= link_to 'Edit', edit_market_path(@market) %> |
<%= link_to 'Back', markets_path %>
